{"generated": "2026-07-24 14:15", "curation": {"market": "개인 투자자 여러분,\n\n지난 24시간 동안 시장은 여러 악재가 복합적으로 작용하며 큰 변동성을 보였습니다. 주요 테마를 중심으로 시장 상황을 브리핑해 드립니다.\n\n<b>중동 지정학적 리스크와 고유가 압력</b>\n중동 지역의 긴장 재점화로 국제유가가 급등하며 시장 전반에 하방 압력을 가했습니다. 유가 100달러 돌파는 인플레이션 우려를 키우고 금리 인상 가능성을 높여 투자 심리를 위축시켰습니다. 이는 국내외 증시 하락의 주요 원인이 되었습니다. [<a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#1</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#2</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiX0FVX3lxTE9MWUM4ZUhFVWhqQjM2V0RmMW54WGxhMUlQUUFTSzBjeU4zbF9CY3dVcm5VdUZOSktCakNRcUk1MmlWcGFHellXaDJlX0NOMEwzUW5NNm9kZURFc3Exc3Bn?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#6</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiXkFVX3lxTFB4VWpTcUxJWmdGTmNiMklzcmw4VnB4bUhSdThteGcxNU5ZRkpGVGFwdlNPWXlxT0hDV1Zyb1pXZWNITXpuOHkwWWIyaTFhVU9hTmJWcDlpekNZQnpTa1E?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#12</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiW0FVX3lxTE96amZqbGMwMFY3b1N2TG5jcldtZHFlQXJlQU5NeHk5VmYyRUI2M2NweFJQVWNEclV3N1NPWmFGX3dhNjhHVVVfclRqbnI1ZHBLMmZqMU9nSHItLWc?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#22</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiXkFVX3lxTFBidW9yOFNqa3UzemZOUXNSbVpUYlBLemF4R2EzZGFQMks3UXRrdVB2Y195ZnBJY0tRMFE1VFdoVExYOURqbzlxVWRYRUo4X01oZWExTVlzemZWLUdBaWc?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#23</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMia0FVX3lxTE12RnhuU19aejNyZU9PNW14b3Rzb0Qyc0NtVFpLODdYSVYwemVxQzkxQWVGTjJyMlpkMzdvajZ2dnFhQ2k0UnVHQU1fSDNETTF4cGhrRzBneUZGWUtQWGRHZDZjUTVYYmIxdkow?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#31</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiYEFVX3lxTE5kejZrZVNJQlZlTHIwcEFadmFZWFZrcVc0MFRYMEJJeFJzSGMtS3cycG5ITHplUVhDdzJyT0tHaE02dTFkN05Dbkx2UVM4bl9xMDYxdGxCUGx6UDRIU19VQw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#33</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiZEFVX3lxTE5CWEwtREFzbmh3Zjl4Z1BNcE5uVVpkTkVHR3lBZDRCMG9ETW80ai10Nk45eGpUdEZmcHIyMWhoU